How to clean wooden spoons
item.description: How do you clean and sanitize wooden spoons? To sanitize your spoons, first clean the spoons with warm, soapy water. Next, lay the spoons on a flat surface — such as a clean baking sheet — and pour 3 percent hydrogen peroxide over them. Wait fifteen minutes, rinse the spoons off and hang them to dry. How do you deep clean a wooden spoon? Let your spoons soak in equal parts white vinegar and room temperature water overnight to really dig deep into the muck.
